Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.01,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}少し迷って　I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.74,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}軽そうに見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.40,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.45,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無価値じゃない　Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}どんな未来だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:42.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}思い出すべき過去とか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:49.16,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}存在しないこと知っても構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}すれ違っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.57,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.27,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}絆ほど強さ纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.80,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:13.40,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.33,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:02.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已無法再倒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:08.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被賦予的人生腳本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}讓其大放異彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些許迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}儘管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.40,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.45,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那並非徒勞  Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}無論未來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:42.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那本該喚醒的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:49.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算是飄渺的存在又何妨
Comment: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
Comment: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
