Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.27,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}如牽掛般縈繞身旁
Comment: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}能否聽到我的吶喊
